summary: Adds a chest, a fireplace, a bedroll and some clutter to an abandoned house in Winterhold. New characters now have a place to store items and sleep without eliminating the need to buy a proper house.
descriptionHtml:
- Description -

Adds a chest, a fireplace, a bedroll and some clutter to an abandoned house in Winterhold. New characters now have a free place to store items and sleep without eliminating the need to buy a proper house.
author: elderfan201
